        "DisplayName" : "GetCurrentDateTime",
        "Expression" : "let today = new Date();\nlet dd = today.getDate();\nlet MMM = today.toLocaleString(\"en\", { month: \"short\" });\nlet YYYY = today.getFullYear();\n\n// 12-hour format\nlet time12 = today.toLocaleString(\"en\", { timeStyle: \"short\", hour12: true });\n// 24-hour format\nlet time24 = today.toLocaleString(\"en\", { timeStyle: \"short\", hour12: false });\n\nlet timeZone = today.toLocaleString(\"id\", { timeZoneName: \"short\" });\nlet temp1 = timeZone.split(\" \");\nlet timeZoneStr = temp1[temp1.length - 1];\nOutput = dd + \" \" + MMM + \" \" + YYYY + \", \" + (hour12 ? time12 : time24);",
